card_text: Target 1 "Shaddoll" monster in your GY; Special Summon it in face-up or face-down Defense Position.$NYou can banish this card and 1 "Shaddoll" card from your GY, then activate 1 of these effects;$N●Change 1 face-down monster you control to face-up Defense Position.$N●Change 1 face-up monster you control to face-down Defense Position.$NYou can only use 1 "Resh Shaddoll Incarnation" effect per turn, and only once that turn.
